How to create a button that resets a form (clears input fields)
================================================================

Create the form and create a button with an id and an onclick function.

<input type="button" id="billing" onclick="myFunction()" value="Reset">


Add a script that resets the form
---------------------------------
<!--reset billingform -->


<script>
function myFunction() {
  document.getElementById("billing").reset();
}
</script>
